2014年2月27日，[[Boom!_Studios|Boom! Studios]]宣布，他們正在為電影推出漫畫系列<ref>{{cite web| script-title = en:Boom! Studios Is Bringing ‘Big Trouble In Little China’ Back In Comic Form And More| publisher = Uproxx| date = 2014-02-27| url = http://www.uproxx.com/webculture/2014/02/boom-studios-bringing-big-trouble-little-china-back-comic-form-maybe/| accessdate = 2014-02-27| archive-date = 2014-02-28| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140228135419/http://www.uproxx.com/webculture/2014/02/boom-studios-bringing-big-trouble-little-china-back-comic-form-maybe/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。漫畫是由艾瑞克·鮑威爾與約翰·卡本特共同撰寫，布萊恩·朱利亞負責繪畫。該系列於2014年6月開始發行<ref>{{cite web| title = Jack Burton finds 'Big Trouble' again in new comic| publisher = USA Today| date = 2014-05-09| url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2014/05/07/big-trouble-in-little-china-comic-book-first-look/8710893/| accessdate = 2014-05-09| archive-date = 2014-05-09| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140509042122/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2014/05/07/big-trouble-in-little-china-comic-book-first-look/8710893/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

Boom! Studios於2016年10月推出了《妖魔大鬧唐人街》的傑克·波頓與《[[紐約大逃亡|紐約大逃亡]]》的[[大蛇·普利斯金|大蛇·普利斯金]]的跨界合作漫畫，名為《''Big Trouble in Little China / Escape from New York''》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsarama.com/30118-totally-awesome-hulk-writer-takes-on-totally-craaazy-big-trouble-in-little-china-escape-from-new-york-crossover.html|title=Two Iconic Cult Characters That Look Exactly Alike Cross Over in BIG TROUBLE IN LITTLE CHINA / ESCAPE FROM NEW YORK|publisher=Newsrama|last=Arrant|first=Chris|date=2016-07-13|accessdate=2016-11-25|archive-date=2017-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510090048/http://www.newsarama.com/30118-totally-awesome-hulk-writer-takes-on-totally-craaazy-big-trouble-in-little-china-escape-from-new-york-crossover.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

