== 續集 ==
2015年6月，[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]報導，片商打算重拍《妖魔大鬧唐人街》，並讓[[巨石強森|巨石強森]]來主演傑克·波頓，Seven Bucks Productions的合作夥伴丹尼和海勒姆·賈西亞將擔任監製。{{le|艾許利·米勒 (編劇)|Ashley Miller (screenwriter)|艾許利·米勒}}與{{le|柴克·史坦茲|Zack Stentz}}被聘來為電影撰寫劇本<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thewrap.com/dwayne-the-rock-johnson-to-star-in-big-trouble-in-little-china-remake-exclusive |title=Dwayne 'The Rock' Johnson to Star in 'Big Trouble In Little China' Remake (Exclusive) |publisher=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]] |last=Sneider |first=Jeff |date=2015-06-01 |accessdate=2016-11-25 |archive-date=2018-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181129143026/https://www.thewrap.com/dwayne-the-rock-johnson-to-star-in-big-trouble-in-little-china-remake-exclusive/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]》報導，強森表示卡本特有興趣參與重拍<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/06/08/dwayne-johnson-john-carpenter-big-trouble-remake|title=Dwayne Johnson Wants John Carpenter Involved In Big Trouble In Little China Remake|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|last=Rosen|first=Christopher|date=2015-06-08|accessdate=2016-11-25|archive-date=2018-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180803074202/http://ew.com/article/2015/06/08/dwayne-johnson-john-carpenter-big-trouble-remake/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。卡本特後來說，他認為這言之過早，且他還未與巨石強森談論關於重拍的事宜<ref>Calia, Michael (2015-06-11). [http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2015/06/11/john-carpenter-hasnt-talked-to-dwayne-johnson-about-big-trouble-in-little-china/ "John Carpenter Hasn't Talked to Dwayne Johnson about 'Big Trouble in Little China.'"] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2015/06/11/john-carpenter-hasnt-talked-to-dwayne-johnson-about-big-trouble-in-little-china/ |date=20160714141200 }} ''Blogs.WSJ.com''. Retrieved 2015-10-04.</ref>。

2018年8月，官方證實新版電影為《妖魔大鬧唐人街》的直接續集而非重拍<ref name="ThePlaylist(2018-08-27)">{{cite news|url=https://theplaylist.net/big-trouble-in-little-china-dwayne-johnson-20180827/|title=‘Big Trouble In Little China’ Remake Starring Dwayne Johnson Is Actually A Sequel|last=Barfield|first=Charles|work=The Playlist|date=2018-08-27|accessdate=2018-08-28|archive-date=2018-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828071144/https://theplaylist.net/big-trouble-in-little-china-dwayne-johnson-20180827/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

